{"tid":702890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國醉酒少女頭卡貨車排氣喉 消防出電鋸解救","createTime":"2018-06-15T09:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T09:40:06.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a468dc5ee65ec89de7dc33690eb9c8bd020c7d19","tid":702890,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180615/_2018061516314855047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180615%2F_2018061516314855047.jpg&h=a9b17c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國明尼蘇達州一名少女日前參加音樂節時，懷疑喝醉酒，頭部卡住一輛柴油貨車的超大排氣喉中，最後消防人員出動電鋸鋸斷排氣喉才救出這名少女，過程也被圍觀民眾拍下來放上Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n圍觀民眾也幽默寫住，「你需要多少酒才能讓自己的頭被困在柴油貨車排氣喉中？」。影片中看到少女無奈地用手撐著地板坐在草地上，而頭部則離奇地卡住貨車排氣喉中動彈不得，消防員則拿著電鋸鑽進車底下準備將排氣喉鋸下來。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警方表示，該名少女被救出來後，因未成年飲酒被警方押送至警局</span>，在為期2天的活動中，還有其他24名未成年人涉飲酒被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n短短9秒鐘的影片，吸引超過332萬人次觀看。這名少女後來看到大家熱烈回響，也在自己臉書貼了一張自己拿著被鋸斷的排氣喉的照片，幽默表示「是的，我就是排氣喉女孩」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/742069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F742069&d=DCzNlVhyL84GmMZ20lFm5C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d8d34da3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F742069&h=f5432481\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/742069</a><br />\n<br />\n點先可以卡到入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15540fdfa6d5e677e170ca7d138ac91adbae39ff","tid":702890,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"唔係雙管黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個頭點塞入去"},{"pid":"6eb598709b9b7a1f367eea378fccf5802f3a908f","tid":702890,"uid":27935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3332dce4935b0c032d305c0c8057fc7ce541f38","tid":702890,"uid":139848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"叫司機坐上去響一響喉噴一噴氣咪成個頭噴返出嚟 仲搞咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}